/PLANETOCOS/GEOMETRY/DetectorAtAltitude 55 km
/PLANETOCOS/GEOMETRY/DetectorAtAltitude 50 km
/PLANETOCOS/GEOMETRY/DetectorAtAltitude 45 km
/PLANETOCOS/GEOMETRY/DetectorAtAltitude 40 km
/PLANETOCOS/GEOMETRY/DetectorAtAltitude 37 km
/PLANETOCOS/GEOMETRY/DetectorAtAltitude 35 km
